        "text": "ElevenLabs starts at $5/month (Starter), Murf at $19/month (Creator), and PlayHT at $31.20/month (Creator). All three offer free tiers: ElevenLabs provides 10K chars/month, Murf offers 10 minutes of voiceover, and PlayHT gives 5K chars/month. ElevenLabs is the most affordable entry point for professional-grade voice generation."
